        <updated>2024-03-17T02:00:48.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-backh="562" data-backw="562" data-imgfileid="100074113" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jopKOlhibRBLVGWCks5Nj9tn3ibNia5c2pBZgAibD23bDmQ0ODXGb83Z1RZFyNB6Hv8gic6K729nBic5nmeCHsW4GvVw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一个月前（2月15日），Sora和 Gemini 1.5 同时推出，这个故事很多人都听过了，Google 被冠以 AI 界汪峰的名头。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">人们纷纷震惊于 Sora 的强大，讨论 Sora 是不是世界模型。而 Gemini 1.5 的第一个模型 Gemini 1.5 Pro 在发布后没多久就逐渐无人问津了。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">当时 Gemini 1.5 Pro 只开放了 Waitlist，一直没能上手测倒是成了一块心病。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最近 Gemini 1.5 Pro 迎来一波大规模开放测试，当时排队的基本都能使用了，有些没有邮件通知，朋友们都可去看看。</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">链接 ：https://aistudio.google.com/</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="242" data-backw="562" data-height="1286" data-imgfileid="100074098" data-ratio="0.4305555555555556" data-type="png" data-w="1080" data-width="2986" style="border-radius: 18px;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Rb7ZpuicwzTcLhMWoNLeQZsibwvbQ8wzyGFv1WRDH3PvvAvwic70b8yib6rMdUlyLsiaa3ZGhVXiacJNbA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">Gemini 1.5 Pro 最大的特点就是10M 上下文与多模态理解相互搭配，实现超强的检索和学习能力，我们也就围绕这两点，问了他五个问题</span><br></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-change: transform;"><div style="margin: 48px 8px 24px;"><div style="padding-left: 30px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin-bottom: -30px;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 30px;height: 30px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 100%;border-style: none;border-color: rgba(118, 178, 124, 0);background-color: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);"><div powered-by="xiumi.us"><p><br></p></div></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="transform: translate3d(-15px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);"><p><strong>问题一：88 万字的《三体》，后续故事怎么发展？</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">我们向Gemini提供了长达约88万字的科幻小说《三体》，它可以根据小说的题材重新编写一版新的小说大纲，从背景设定、主要人物、情节梗概、主题设定到小说结局它可以非常有逻辑地完成。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">另外对于《三体》的开放式结局它也可以继续扩写，在充分地满足大家的各种想象的同时又不脱离原著。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="897" data-backw="562" data-height="1607" data-imgfileid="100074100" data-ratio="1.595829195630586" data-type="png" data-w="1007" data-width="1007" style="border-radius: 18px;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Rb7ZpuicwzTcLhMWoNLeQZsqOEuyvuiaPGa3XpXkRJIZ6qOiccXD9hoYGjZx2RNYIJ7XkCMibQbiapR2Q/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><div style="margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-size: 16px;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="will-change: transform;"><div style="margin: 48px 8px 24px;"><div style="padding-left: 30px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="margin-bottom: -30px;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="display: inline-block;width: 30px;height: 30px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-radius: 100%;border-style: none;border-color: rgba(118, 178, 124, 0);background-color: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);"><div powered-by="xiumi.us"><p><br></p></div></div></div><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="transform: translate3d(-15px, 0px, 0px);"><div style="padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;vertical-align: top;"><div powered-by="xiumi.us" style="font-size: 20px;color: rgb(55, 80, 114);"><p><strong>问题二：20篇论文，哪篇更有价值？</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">我们选取了20篇神经网络相关的英文学术文章。Gemini 不仅能够对各种细节问题对答如流，而且还能够非常有条理有逻辑地整理出最具参考价值的学术论文。</span></p><p style="margin: 24px 8px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;">各位研究学者们再也不用熬夜看文献写报告了！你们的头发有救啦！</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></p><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-backh="1252" data-backw="562" data-height="2265" data-imgfileid="100074101" data-ratio="2.2271386430678466" data-type="png" data-w="1017" data-width="1017" style="border-radius: 18px;width: 100%;height: auto;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5gR6KWHNb7Rb7ZpuicwzTcLhMWoNLeQZseRg67Uv1FibrjzSctkxQqFdox5rmKNY2WtO1ABqA6YUADibibjhpyVsFg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;"><span style="color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-family: PingFangSC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.1px;text-align: start;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-b